00b3504f18fa63b5","tid":1307352,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc853abdc0af3eafcfd9f6d8243de70822a2003c","tid":1307352,"uid":97050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"冇食藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"冇啊 食藥冇用架只係禁住一排唔發 其實只要身體好免疫力強就唔會有濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:31:01.000Z","msg":"聽人講係免疫力太勁先會有濕疹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"我自己就做過兩次敏感測試，兩次結果都唔同，問過醫生點解，佢話係會隨住年紀而有改變。細個做果次係連飯都唔食得，但大個做果次就蝦蟹果啲海鮮係唔食得，但牛、蛋果啲係可以食，所以我依家都冇乜點戒口。<br />\n<br />\n食藥方面就唔可能郁啲就食類固醇，因為停左藥之後返發會勁好多，我自己都經歷過。依家我就睇緊鄰居介紹既醫生，佢唔會比類固醇，只會比啲抗過敏同止痕既藥，如果你有傷口就會比消炎藥。同埋藥膏佢就話係自己調製既，唔知有冇類固醇。"},{"pid":"c7d9f5ebc895125623f962a5518e9813b8e3a118","tid":1307352,"uid":97050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f60ad775f32cbe19bd15842712d53dd0fd2547","tid":1307352,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"打少d j 認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"冇j點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cc9891727ad1cd02df264555bf15acd5116f2d","tid":1307352,"uid":97050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35e292efa5a3359e23ba1c1c2e2e22d308ff89ed","tid":1307352,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32c317cf07ea63fbeaed00a538eaf44d8048c276","tid":1307352,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f56c3af9d1c91aa4070bf4700b3504f18fa63b5","tid":1307352,"uid":163962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"冇啊 食藥冇用架只係禁住一排唔發 其實只要身體好免疫力強就唔會有濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"藥高我都冇搽 痴lum lum 又唔係太止到痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h